with version stable 0.11.3d 0.11.3c 0.11.3b 0.11.3a 0.11.3
with base    kdelibs-v4 MPlayer
with elect   ffmpeg           '' ''                  for frontend for ffmpeg and broadcasting/recording http streams
with elect   gst-plugins-base '' --without-gstreamer to use GStreamer as multimedia backend
with elect   xine-lib         '' --without-xine      to play DVD
with also    -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX:PATH=/usr
with also    -DCMAKE_INSTALL_RPATH:PATH=/usr/lib64:/usr/lib
with also    -DCMAKE_SKIP_BUILD_RPATH:BOOL=TRUE
with also    -DCMAKE_BUILD_WITH_INSTALL_RPATH:BOOL=TRUE
with also    -DCMAKE_INSTALL_RPATH_USE_LINK_PATH:BOOL=TRUE
with also    -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release
with role    audio/player video/dvd video/player kde-extragear
with trait   kde4
with source  http://kmplayer.kde.org/pkgs/kmplayer-$VERSION.tar.bz2
with info    last 20120614
with info    home http://kmplayer.kde.org/
with info    cite 'video player plugin for Konqueror
and basic MPlayer/Xine/ffmpeg/ffserver/VDR frontend for KDE'
